snippet.title: Zapling Bygone Deluxe Edition - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
We have some very exciting news to share at Jandusoft today!

We've teamed up with our partners Tesura Games to create a special physical edition for our metroidvania game, Zapling Bygone, developed by the talented solodev 9FingerGames.

The Zapling Bygone physical edition will be available soon on both Playstation 4 and Playstation 5 consoles, with two different editions to choose from.

The Zapling Bygone Deluxe Edition will include:

Physical Game
Original Soundtrack
Zapling Pin
Mini Cómics
Collector's Box

This edition is perfect for die-hard fans of the game who want to have a physical collection of their favorite game.

More info: https://www.jandusoft.com/zaplingbygone
